<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Property Pending Approval</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .property-details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 0.8;
        }
        .header, .footer {
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fc6600, #fc6600);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="header">Let's Stay Connected! Contact Details Inside!</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= cusName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your interest in our property listings! Below are the details you requested:</p>
        <strong>Owner Contact Information:</strong>
        <p class="contact-info">
            <span>Name:</span> <strong> <%= onwerName %></strong>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-info">
            <span>Email:</span> <strong><%= email %></strong>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-info">
            <span>Phone Number:</span> <strong><%= phone %></strong>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-info">
            <span>Property Name:</span> <strong><%= propertyName %></strong>
          </p>
          <p class="contact-info">
            <span>Address:</span> <strong><%= address %></strong>
          </p>
            <p>We hope these details are helpful. If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@8sqft.com">support@8sqft.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Looking forward to assisting you in finding your perfect property.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing 8SQFT</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p> <strong>8sqft Team</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
